<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ḥbẗ mlạ qlby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - ḥbẗ mlạ qlby bṣlybẗ njạny

[V2]
 ʿạysẖ wạlyẗ ḥby ạlly ḥml ạḥzạny

[V3]
 1- fạkr ywm mạ ạkẖrjny mn byt ạlʿbwdyẗ

[V4]
 lmạ jh wmạt ʿny wḥrrny mn ạlkẖṭyẗ

[V5]
 2- mytẖạqy mytẖạq ạlslạm mn ʿnd ạlhy wrby

[V6]
 ạlly ḥạrsny wmạ bynạm whw fy gẖrbty sndy

[V7]
 3- mạsẖy mʿạyạ fy ạlṭryq mạ ynsy wlạ ytrkny

[V8]
 ʿmry mạ ạsẖwf zyẗ ṣdyq ạbdạ mạ ạtkẖly ʿny

[V9]
 4- hw ạlhy ạlly ṣạnʿny hw ạlḥy ạly ạlạbd

[V10]
 hw ạlly ʿmlny wạnsẖạỷny wḥbny ạly ạlạbd</lyrics>
<author>ʿạdl ḥbyb, ʿạdl ḥbyb</author>
<hymn_number>10363</hymn_number>
</song>